name: token-attacher-compendium-example
title: Token Attacher Auto Import JSON Compendium Example
description: This Example module has two compendiums in the form of json files exported through Token Attacher.When you open the compendium tab it'll ask to import them into the world independent of the current system.When the module version changes it'll ask to import the compendiums again, deleteing the pervious ones.
